I think arugula stands up better to the trout vs. watercress. I would probably use less than 6 oz., however. I found Chinese buttercrunch (farmer's market) which is mild like Bibb lettuce and it worked pretty well. This was a nice no-fuss summertime dinner that my 5 year-old gave 5 stars.

